http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ziy3fYi_0eE

FEATURED PRODUCTS:

-Milani Eyeshadow Primer
-L'oreal Infallible Eyeshadow in Bronzed Taupe
-Milani Eye Tech Extreme in Blackest Black
-Rimmel ScandalEyes in Nude (inner rim)
-Almay Get Up & Grow Mascara
-Maybelline Lash Discovery Mascara

Brushes I used: 
-Sigma E55 flat brush - $10 http://bit.ly/E55emily
(flat brush for patting on shadow)

-Sigma E25 - $10 http://bit.ly/E25blending
(used for apply/blending shadow in crease)

-Sigma E40 - $12 http://bit.ly/e40emily
(used bare to blend out shadow)

-Sigma E21 smudge - $10 http://bit.ly/e21emily
(used to smudge shadow on lower lashline)

(Sigma links are affiliate links)

-Lips: ELF Studio Lip Balm in Rose

Other info:
Nails: Red from YSL (not sure of exact shade name)
Shirt: JC Penney
Earrings: Claire's

Music by Josef Horhay: http://bit.ly/josefmusic
